<subSubSection pageId="122" pageNumber="123" type="distinguishing features">
<paragraph pageId="122" pageNumber="123">Distinguishing features.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="122" pageNumber="123">The type variety has small leaves and bracts 0.5-1.5 cm long, equalling or only slightly exceeding the flower heads. The corollas are only 7-8 mm long.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
